ve coverage\nchangeover that can be visualized as a traveling wave. A single pattern of\noscillations in the NO+H2 reaction includes the key role of intermediate NHad\nspecies providing the catalytic removal of strongly bound nitrogen. The driving\nforces, the feedback, and chemical interactions within the traveling waves are\nclearly understood.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 May 2016 04:54:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-19"}
