e layer are\nstill ongoing, and we stress that, under this circumstance, the phenomenology\nand characteristic scales for fragmentation of the layer are fundamentally\ndifferent from those derived traditionally for pre-existing layers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 May 2016 15:36:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-20"}
